name: CuteSexyRobutts style (TEXTUAL INVERSION)
description:
Appreciate my work? Can you buy me a coffe please :)

First of all, I know that several models of this style have already been uploaded, but if I'm not mistaken, not in this TEXTUAL INVERSION format, I don't want to compare myself against the other models either, I just want to share my model since I really like the drawing style from CuteSexyRobutts I hope you like it too thanks.

I named this model v2, since it was a second training session that I thought was very close to the artist's style but it would be like version 1.

I haven't tried it with other models, so far I've only tried it with YuzuGinger, I suppose it can be used with models that have a good training of Anime images in the background, I don't know if it works with realistic style models.

QR to my page buymeacoffee
